show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: After her daughter dies in a tragic school collapse, a woman discovers her husband chose to save another child — the daughter of his first love. Betrayed and grieving, she files for divorce and begins her calculated descent into revenge.
